## 1. Tailwind Plus Template (Spotlight)

The base template and components from Tailwind Plus are subject to the Tailwind Plus Personal License.
See [LICENSE-TAILWIND.md](./LICENSE-TAILWIND.md) for the full license terms.

**Copyright © Tailwind Labs Inc.**

The following directories and files are derived from the Tailwind Plus Spotlight template:
- Base structure of `/src/components/` (original components)
- Base structure of `/src/app/` (routing and layout patterns)
- `/src/styles/` (Tailwind CSS configurations)
- Original design patterns and UI components

